411
00:32:09,667 --> 00:32:11,067
Nada?

412
00:32:11,068 --> 00:32:13,944
De fazer algo? Ouvir algo?

413
00:32:13,945 --> 00:32:15,193
Lembra de descer?

414
00:32:15,194 --> 00:32:16,650
Nada.

415
00:32:16,651 --> 00:32:18,983
Então, você acordou.

416
00:32:18,984 --> 00:32:20,982
Subiu até o quarto.

417
00:32:20,983 --> 00:32:22,651
